    <div class="main review-item" id="1167257">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1167257/" class="title-link">还《大学》原貌</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1167257"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/lilylee/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1254533-4.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/lilylee/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">凡石</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2007-06-13"
      class="main-meta">2007-06-13 21:43:05</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1167257_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  我以前看的《大学》是朱熹的评注本，买到南怀瑾先生的这本书，才见到真正《大学》古本原貌，南怀瑾先生博学多才，对《大学》的理解深刻而且广博。他推翻了沿袭千年的对《大学》三纲领，八条目的理解。  建议大家不要只看别人的评说，要读读原文，拾别人的牙慧永远都不会有真正...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1167257/#comments">(7回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">4有用 / 1没用</span>
                        <span class="publisher left">
                            世界知识出版社1998版</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
